{"tid":1787113,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［培正小學］ 隱瞞流感大爆發！！！","createTime":"2019-12-17T16:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T16:57:12.000Z","uid":286576,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"40d29d98c98d7394aa45fa5f7915254e9a01939a","tid":1787113,"uid":286576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:09:41.000Z","msg":"我是培正小學的家長，一年級有超過10名學童在一兩天前確診流感，當中有多個小朋友高燒等嚴重症狀。<br />\n<br />\n有傳染病爆發很正常，不過學校老師處理真有問題。 因為星期四（兩天後）要考試,老師竟然要已請病假的同學，如沒有症狀，就要回校考試。而我們只可以在家長群組中收到消息，學校連一個電郵也沒有通佈，要我們預防一下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實是老師欠缺對傳染病的認知，還是學校給老師壓力，還是教育局給學校壓力，一定要小朋友帶病考試呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下是老師的whatsapp：<br />\n<br />\n&rdquo;如果小朋友身體情況許可, 或已退燒, 未考口試的也盡量讓學生在星期四前回校補考口試 🙏&ldquo;"},{"pid":"13d7ddcb9b33d5cefb4f5e5ad95b7335b22424c7","tid":1787113,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一屆「和你影」攝影比賽 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786771</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a01ee403f22bd29277e4893e9baeefde28d3cb31","tid":1787113,"uid":286576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13d7ddcb9b33d5cefb4f5e5ad95b7335b22424c7","tid":1787113,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一屆「和你影」攝影比賽 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786771</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:33:59.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"d31d8780892ae3e66f63f8fde098e42a96708721","tid":1787113,"uid":148473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:34:15.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\